Question: One image shows balloons on strings that gather to a point against a blue sky, but no one holding the balloons.

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there balloons on strings that gather to a point against a blue sky?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there balloons on strings that gather to a point against a blue sky?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there someone holding the balloons?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there someone holding the balloons?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
